{"tid":2457220,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[奉上減壓gif]親愛嘅巴絲們，小弟需要你地嘅支持","createTime":"2021-03-22T12:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T14:03:26.000Z","uid":372421,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c20dd736553df4f7d5617e4809d3922f25ae7ccb","tid":2457220,"uid":372421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:45:23.000Z","msg":"上一個post，我唔識規距無放圖。經各位巴絲指導後，補宜家補返喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就做梗一項研究，想睇吓究竟online learning嘅環境底下，你嘅上堂環境同你嘅自身能力對你嘅學業成績邊樣重要啲，點樣重要法，然而你地嘅答覆就會幫我了解到最後所引伸嘅education inequality 嘅問題，一切資料絕對保密！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係讀梗HD/ASSO/學士學位，而過去兩個sem又超過9成時間係online上堂，咁你嘅經歷就可以幫到我呢個FYP喇！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問卷link：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/yGsc6Am9pmfQqsCR8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyGsc6Am9pmfQqsCR8&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=24e3594d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yGsc6Am9pmfQqsCR8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望巴絲多多支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日不定時更新，小小心意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇完開心嘅就幫下手填喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/qaZEU8wBXtbJwX8R25NnMRJO2AY=/1000x0/filters:no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/12483305/Rz3kECVjTVWsi25SEsAK_Bulls_Eye_Mouth.0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FqaZEU8wBXtbJwX8R25NnMRJO2AY%3D%2F1000x0%2Ffilters%3Ano_upscale%28%29%2Fcdn.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_asset%2Ffile%2F12483305%2FRz3kECVjTVWsi25SEsAK_Bulls_Eye_Mouth.0.gif&h=64bce689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8fmYDX8q-Z93zWXgZP44DK4w1ks=/1000x0/filters:no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_